{"title":"五月村庄","authors":["乙影"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）庄头望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚热的天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋风围着老杨树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打圈圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子莠了穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡好喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再转一转水车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇浇田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垄沟里的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白晃晃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天多出点力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天多打点粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）畦子地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"畦子地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五亩七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——隔壁张大妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前年分得的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前咱们哪有地？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的穷人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是好福气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从咱家分了畦子地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早起趟（贪）黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘儿几个一齐卖力气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年有点小积蓄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天买了条小毛驴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）生产支有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小毛驴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用劲转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇完麦田浇菜田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇了园子好防旱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——参加今年大生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿福嫂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐地边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手摇纺车心盘算："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝汗衫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给前线战士穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水车转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺车转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多生产，多支前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放全中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙有光沾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——多喜欢！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}